    "Do not infer from this discussion that Charlie and I are going anywhere; we continue to be in excellent health, and we love what we do.",
    "The first law of capital allocation is that what is smart at one price is dumb at another.",
    "Housing will come back \u2013 you can be sure of that.",
    "America\u2019s best days lie ahead.",
    ],
    featured: false,
    sourceUrl: 'https://www.berkshirehathaway.com/letters/2011ltr.pdf',
    readingTimeMinutes: 15,
