<p>Intrinsic Business Value</p>
<p>Charlie and I measure our performance by the rate of gain in Berkshire’s per-share intrinsic business</p>
<p>value. If our gain over time outstrips the performance of the S&P 500, we have earned our paychecks. If it</p>
<p>doesn’t,weareoverpaidatanyprice.</p>
<p>Wehavenowaytopinpointintrinsicvalue. Butwedohaveauseful,thoughconsiderablyunderstated,</p>
