<p>was$46million.(Despitethesizeofourposition,weexercisednocontroloveroperations.)</p>
<p>Wethenpurchasedtheremaining50%of GEICOatthebeginningof1996,whichspurred Davy,at95,</p>
<p>to make a video tape saying how happy he was that his beloved GEICO would permanently reside with</p>
