<p>thatareinappropriate inrelation toourresources. Indeed,wearefarmoreconservative thanmostlarge insurers</p>
<p>inthatrespect. Inthepastyear,Ajithassignificantlyincreasedhislifereinsuranceoperation,developingannual</p>
<p>premiumvolumeofabout$2billionthatwillrepeatfordecades.</p>
<p>From a standing start in 1985, Ajit has created an insurance business with float of $30 billion and</p>
