<p>Eventhough Net Jetswasconsistentlyarunawaywinnerwithcustomers,ourfinancialresults,sinceits</p>
<p>acquisitionin1998,wereafailure. Inthe11yearsthrough2009,thecompanyreportedanaggregatepre-taxloss</p>
<p>of$157million,afigurethatwasfarunderstatedsinceborrowingcostsat Net Jetswereheavilysubsidizedbyits</p>
