<p>Anumberofgoodthingshappenedat Berkshirelastyear,butlet’sfirstgetthebadnewsoutoftheway.</p>
<p>When the partnership I ran took control of Berkshire in 1965, I could never have dreamed that a year in</p>
<p>whichwehadagainof$24.1billionwouldbesubpar,intermsofthecomparisonwepresentonthefacing</p>
<p>page.</p>
