<p>Berkshire’s ownership interest in all four companies is likely to increase in the future. Mae West had it</p>
<p>right:“Toomuchofagoodthingcanbewonderful.”</p>
<p>The four companies possess marvelous businesses and are run by managers who are both talented and</p>
<p>shareholder-oriented. At Berkshire we much prefer owning a non-controlling but substantial portion of a</p>
